\begin_layout Standard
Vi skal have data for 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(Y_{t}^{H},P_{t}^{Z},Z_{t}\right)$
\end_inset

 på top-niveau og 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(c_{q,a,t},P_{q,a,t}^{\text{}},Q_{q,a,t},M_{q,a,t},X_{q,a,t},r_{t}\right)$
\end_inset

